\newlabel{fig:source_type}{{6}{2}{Detection accuracy by source text type. Both human-crafted and Auditor-generated texts yield identical accuracy (59.3\%), suggesting the APE-style refinement matches human-designed linguistic traps}{figure.caption.7}{}}
